Hello!  This is a software project called Social-Garden.  It aims to create an optimized flow network to create a planetary-wide nervous system.  It's aim is high: a maximally collaborative, minimally superfluous, peer-to-peer system of sharing information and creative expressions to foster a beautiful, self-organizing, fractal economy of information and knowledge.  Your ideas and contributions are desired, and thanks for your interest.  

Documentation is currently on the project wiki at github.org.

This Software is licensed under the GNU Public License version 3.

This project is sponsored at github.org and is in partnership with nodilus.org.  Please support them, too!

Cheers!

Mark Janssen
